scrssi(1)
==========

NAME
----
scrssi - Screen+irssi daemon for Archlinux

SYNOPSIS
--------
Activate the daemon
*rc.d start scrssi*
Stop the daemon
*rc.d stop scrssi*

Execute client
*scrssi*

DESCRIPTION
-----------
*scrssi* define a daemon for Archlinux used to activate a session of scree+irssi.

TIPS & TRICKS
-------------
Use irssi with bitlbee to manage all your IM account directly throught a IRC gateway.
The daemon of *scrssi* allows to activate/disable of your account.
That's great!


FILES
-----
*scrssi* uses the file '/etc/scrssirc' that is a config file for screen used to activate irssi once the session 
of *scrssi* will be activated.

